  • Acid-free paper won't yellow or fade over time.

  • Includes basic inside delivery or dock delivery. Receiving staff is responsible for delivering the product to the inside end user. Basic Inside Delivery requirements: First floor receiving area only. Basic inside delivery includes lift-gate truck and simple inside delivery – simple inside delivery is moving the pallet off the truck to a first-floor receiving area. Entryway must be a least 48” wide. It does not include (1) breaking down the pallet to make the delivery, (2) making multiple deliveries within the account, or (3) stacking the product on a shelf.
  • 20-lb paper with 500 sheets per ream, 10 reams per carton and 40 cartons.
